ClamAV::Client 0.11
A client class for the ClamAV `clamd` virus scanner daemon.
(C) 2004-2005 Julian Mehnle <julian@mehnle.net>
<http://www.mehnle.net/software/clamav-client>
==============================================================================

ClamAV::Client is a class acting as a client for a ClamAV `clamd` virus scanner
daemon.  The daemon may run locally or on a remote system as ClamAV::Client can
use both Unix domain sockets and TCP/IP sockets.  The full functionality of
the `clamd` client/server protocol is supported.

